songs.title: ​gunagaar (sinner)
songs.lyrics:
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!

Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!

Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar... aah aah

Dikhayi dinde ajnabee menu duniya ch charo passe..
Nindran ni aan menu bistre ch paltan passe...
Nasha menu hunda ni shraab to
Hennessy pinde saver ho gayi raat to...
Zindagi jive rabb russa meri zaat to...
Raje ve tu yarran kolo akka rehnda kato
Puchde yaar mere, dil de taar tutte sare
Main gaddi vich baitha gina tare
Peewan bhang likhan geet
Mere yaar mere meet
Kinne jail ch band
Kinne bech de bhang
Kinne chitta pakande
Kinne paisa kamande
Kinne bhukhe reh k tang hoke goliyan chalande..
Sanu labh di Phiray POLICE ve jado da main jameya main 420sss
840 din raat maine paap kamaye..
Ve des chad appa jado di pardes aaye.... use din da

Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...

Burrraaa burrraa...!

Pawaan goliyan bandook ch
Geet likhan kitaab ch
Galiyan ch kooka galan kadda gal baat ch..
Bhang de nashe ch bhule sare gam menu...
Dola main shraab bichre yaran di yaad ch..
Apan gore aadmi de desh ch abaad
Dinda ni koi sath jado desh udo aanda yaad..
Peewan main shraab peewan bhang ude baaad aape baithan kalla jagan sari raat..
Honde savere maran verriyan di galian de gere..
Hathi dunalli bandook labhan dusmna nu mere jehre
Pith piche karan gallan batheriyan
Oh mohre aake khangde ni mere..
Haraaaamkhorrroooo
Niklo bahar aake karo mera samna main veriyan de buhe te khlo k pukaarna..
Jado da aaya vilait, gore aadmi di kaid ch band..
Bas iko usi dino da rehnda han main........

Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
Main duniya to hoke tang peewan bhang rehna...
Gharo bahar, gunagaar,labhan menu thanedaar....!
